<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-legal-ombudsman> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Legal Ombudsman for England and Wales is appointed by the Office for Legal Complaints to run an independent scheme that resolves complaints about lawyers in a fair and effective way, helping to drive improvements to legal services. The Legal Ombudsman works with the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
